configurable via `PORT` environment variable)\n- **Static Files**: Serves files from the `public/` directory\n\n**Data Sources & Functions:**\n\n1. **Bitcoin (BTC) via CoinGecko API** (FREE, no key required)\n   - `getBTCPrice()`: Fetches current BTC price in USD with 24-hour change\n   - `getBTCHistory(days)`: Fetches BTC historical prices for specified days\n\n2. **Gold Futures (GC=F) via Yahoo Finance API**\n   - `getYahooPrice(symbol)`: Fetches current price with change percentage\n   - `getYahooHistory(symbol, range, interval)`: Fetches historical data\n\n3. **S&P 500 Index (^GSPC) via Yahoo Finance API**\n   - Uses same functions as Gold with different symbols\n\n**API Endpoints:**\n- `GET /api/prices` - Returns current prices for BTC, Gold, and S&P 500\n- `GET /api/history/:asset` - Returns historical data for specified asset\n  - Parameters: `range` query parameter (1d, 1w, 1m, 3m, 1y)\n  - Assets: btc, gold, spx\n\n**Range Configuration:**\n```\n1d  → 1 day data at 5-minute intervals\n1w  → 7 days data at 1-hour intervals\n1m  → 30 days data at 1-day intervals\n3m  → 90 days data at 1-day intervals\n1y  → 365 days data at 1-week intervals\n```\n\n### 4. Frontend HTML File\n\n**File: `/home/ubuntu/my-project/index.html`** (COMPLETE CONTENT - 547 lines)\n\nThis is a sophisticated, modern web dashboard written in Chinese (全球市场行情 = Global Market Dashboard). \n\n**Key Components:**\n\n1. **Header Section**\n   - Logo with icon and title\n   - Last update timestamp\n   - Auto-refresh countdown (60 seconds)\n   - Manual refresh button\n\n2. **Price Cards Grid (3 columns, responsive)**\n   - BTC Card: Shows Bitcoin price with 24-hour change\n   - Gold Card: Shows Gold Futures price with change\n   - S&P 500 Card: Shows index price with change\n   - Each card displays:\n     - Asset icon/emoji\n     - Current price (formatted with colors)\n     - Percentage change (green for up, red for down)\n     - Absolute price change\n     - Flash animation on updates\n\n3. **Charts Section (3 interactive charts using Chart.js)**\n   - BTC/USD 走势 (BTC/USD Trend)\n   - 黄金期货 (Gold Futures) - GC=F USD/oz\n   - 标普500指数 (S&P 500 Index) - ^GSPC\n   \n   Each chart has:\n   - Time range buttons: 1D, 1W, 1M (default), 3M, 1Y\n   - Line charts with gradient fill (green for up trends, red for down trends)\n   - Tooltips showing formatted prices with dates\n   - Loading spinner overlay\n   - Error handling\n\n**Styling:**\n- Dark theme (dark blue/purple background)\n- Modern design with glass-morphism effects\n- Color scheme:\n  - BTC: #f7931a (orange)\n  - Gold: #fbbf24 (amber)\n  - S&P 500: #60a5fa (blue)\n  - Up trend: #00c98b (green)\n  - Down trend: #ff4d5e (red)\n\n**JavaScript Functionality:**\n- Auto-refresh prices every 60 seconds\n- Manual refresh for all data\n- Chart switching between time ranges\n- Real-time price formatting\n- Error handling and user feedback\n- Responsive design (adapts to mobile)\n\n### 5. Static Files\n\n**File: `/home/ubuntu/my-project/public/index.html`**\nThis is a duplicate of `/home/ubuntu/my-project/index.html` (identical 547 lines)\n\n### 6. API Endpoints Summary\n\n| Endpoint | Method | Query Params | Returns | Assets |\n|----------|--------|--------------|---------|--------|\n| `/api/prices` | GET | - | Current prices + 24h change | BTC, Gold, S&P500 |\n| `/api/history/:asset` | GET | `range` (1d,1w,1m,3m,1y) | Historical price data points | btc, gold, spx |\n\n### 7. Test Files (Not Part of Main Application)\n\n- `hello.py` - Python \"Hello, World!\"\n- `hello.js` - JavaScript console log\n- `hello.html` - Basic HTML page\n- `hello.cpp` - C++ program that writes to tmp.txt\n- `tmp.txt` - Output from hello.cpp\n- `71bb7ba23ef6e6d577762960386d0b9f.txt` - Contains a hash (likely git-related)\n\n### 8. Configuration & Database\n\n**No Configuration Files Found:**\n- No `.env` file\n- No database configuration\n- No environment-specific configs\n- Uses hardcoded external APIs (CoinGecko, Yahoo Finance)\n\n**No 